    "We use Zipf's Law to see if the probabilities calculated above correspond to the probabilities by Zipf's Law.\n",
    "We divide the constant value by the rank of the word, to get the Zipf's probability of this word.\n",
    "This is what can be seen down there."
   ]
  },
